headline: GTA Online
subtitle: GOOD CALL
content:
F. Clinton & Partner gaining a rep? Franklin has some jobs that are strictly off the books.

He’s got the targets; you’ve got the skills. Add some flair to those hits and you’ll land yourself a well-earned bonus. Yes, it’s assassination, but you can make it art.

Answer ringing payphones across Los Santos and Blaine County to pick up Payphone Hits.
